Vuuri
Home Docs GitHub

The Vue Muuri Integration

$ yarn add vuuri

Usage

<vuuri :items="items">
  <template #item="{ item }">
    <YourComponent :item="item" />
  </template>
</vuuri>

Automatic CRUD Updates

You just worry about writing javascript

// adding
this.items.push(newItem);

// removing
this.items.splice(1, 0);

Vuuri takes care of the rest

Credits

Vuuri is a simple wrapper for Vue.js and full credits go to the author of the Muuri library: Niklas Rm
